Term-Menu version 0.08
========================

Term::Menu - Print a menu to the screen and ask for an answer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no modules, but the following modules are optional:

  Test::Expect (to test)

